info.name: Parking Data Specification - Static
info.description: Parking Static data standard defines a common format to share static information from various parking locations within the defined zone. It provides information on various parking complex, parking lots, kind of infrastructure, access policies, entry / exit gate information, reservation information and tariffs. This data standard is based on Protocol Buffers. The hierarchy of elements and their type definitions are specified in the linked .proto file.
